### Seller Portfolio API Tests
### Base URL for the API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4080/api/v1
@token = {{loginResponse.response.body.token}}

### ===============================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ===============================

# @name loginResponse
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@cody.inc",
  "password": "password"
}

### ===============================
### SELLER PORTFOLIO CRUD
### ===============================

### Create a portfolio item
# @name createPortfolio
POST {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seller_id": 1,
  "title": "E-commerce Website Redesign",
  "description": "Complete redesign of an e-commerce platform with improved UX/UI and mobile responsiveness.",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/images/portfolio/ecommerce-redesign.jpg",
  "project_url": "https://example-ecommerce.com",
  "display_order": 1,
  "status": "Active"
}

### Create another portfolio item
# @name createPortfolio2
POST {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seller_id": 1,
  "title": "Mobile App Development",
  "description": "Cross-platform mobile application for fitness tracking with real-time analytics.",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/images/portfolio/fitness-app.jpg",
  "project_url": "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.example.fitness",
  "display_order": 2,
  "status": "Active"
}

### Get all portfolio items
GET {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get portfolio items by seller ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio?seller_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get portfolio items with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio?seller_id=1&skip=0&take=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get portfolio items with search
GET {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio?search=website
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get portfolio items by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio?status=Active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get portfolio item by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a portfolio item
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "E-commerce Platform Overhaul",
  "description": "Complete overhaul of an e-commerce platform with modern design and enhanced performance."
}

### Delete a portfolio item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/seller-portfolio/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===============================
### SELLER PROFILE PORTFOLIO ENDPOINT
### ===============================

### Get seller's portfolio (via seller profile)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sellers/1/portfolio
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

